Columns: 18;
                                                  ruled lines: 23;
                                                  written lines: 23; Uniform layout. Ruling by hard point,
membrane by membrane. Nine membranes in total, two columns per membrane written within colour-decorated engravings.  Three tagin on שעטנזגץ. Several majuscular and minuscular letters. The names of the sons of Haman arranged in 11 lines, in accordance with the rule. Wooden rollers (290mm high).
